headline.print_headline: Olympiakos Stun Atletico Madrid in Athens
headline.main: Olympiakos Stun Atletico Madrid in Athens

lead_paragraph: Olympiakos Piraeus secured a surprise 3-2 victory over last year’s Champions League runners-up Atletico Madrid to make a dream start to their Group A campaign on Tuesday.
